column1: Baby Barnaby's////Yum!! Such a great brunch spot...I love coming here. I've been enough times to have the menu memorized
column2: which means I've come to settle on getting the Bob's healthy plate every single time now since it's my favorite thing. I usually sub veggie sausage in for the chicken apple in order to make it veg
column3: and it's delish! And yes I can eat six full egg whites...honestly I could probably eat eight of those super fluffy perfect things!! Everything else I've tried is good too...including pancakes
column4: green eggs (with egg whites like I like 'em!)
